0.4.6.name: wordpress/shopperpress-datafeed-importer
0.4.6.description: Use ShopperPress DataFeed Importer to import a csv data file and inject up to 1 million posts in WordPress! It is free to use and has some cool features that other similiar plugins don't with many more cool new ideas coming soon. Developed by Ryan Bayne from WebTechGlobal, a University graduate in 2009. This is a demo.
